    <item>
      <title>博通预测人工智能销售将激增，推动股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-13/broadcom-predicts-ai-sales-surge-pushing-shares-higher</link>
      <description><![CDATA[博通公司在财报发布后的电话会议上预测其人工智能芯片的需求将大幅增长，并表示人工智能产品的销售额将在第一财季增长 65%。汤姆·麦肯齐在彭博电视台报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-13/broadcom-predicts-ai-sales-surge-pushing-shares-higher</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 10:59:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国银行称政治局作出承诺后投资者纷纷买入中国股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/bofa-says-investors-rush-to-china-stocks-after-politburo-pledge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行策略师表示，由于中国领导人承诺采取更多刺激措施促进经济增长，过去一周投资者再次将资金投入中国股市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/bofa-says-investors-rush-to-china-stocks-after-politburo-pledge</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 10:57:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>天然气发电厂拍卖失败，波兰电力市场风险加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/risks-mount-for-polish-power-market-as-gas-units-fail-at-auction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于公用事业公司计划建设的天然气发电机组在一次重要的市场拍卖中未能获得任何支持，波兰在本世纪末将越来越容易出现电力短缺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/risks-mount-for-polish-power-market-as-gas-units-fail-at-auction</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 10:54:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行官员预计进一步降息，维勒鲁瓦支持市场观点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/ecb-s-villeroy-sees-more-cuts-before-rates-no-longer-restrictive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行政策制定者表示，将会进一步降息，法国央行行长弗朗索瓦·维勒鲁瓦德加洛表示，投资者押注降息幅度超过 100 个基点看起来是合理的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/ecb-s-villeroy-sees-more-cuts-before-rates-no-longer-restrictive</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 07:57:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受俄罗斯空袭和制裁前景影响，油价有望每周上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-december-13</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在西方可能加强制裁的情况下，俄罗斯空袭乌克兰，加剧地缘政治紧张局势，油价延续涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-december-13</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 23:30:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
